	Professor at the Chair of Obstetrics and Gynecology at the Institute of Medical Education, Almazov National Medical Research Center.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Member of the International Society of Gynecological Endocrinology (ISGE).
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	The main area of her research work is treatment of hyperandrogenemia in women (polycystic ovarian syndrome, congenital adrenal hyperplasia, hirsutism, acne).
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Master of all current methods of diagnosis and treatment of thyroid, adrenal, pituitary disorders as well as obesity and carbohydrate metabolism correction.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
